{"tid":1017513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"許鞍華首部執導電影《瘋劫》(1979) 修復版藍光","createTime":"2019-02-11T13:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T03:31:46.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8370105d3b1ae8ead8695186080c45350b096ee0","tid":1017513,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201902/10/001256a58cnmv8vramn3y1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201902%2F10%2F001256a58cnmv8vramn3y1.jpg&h=bd924ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n康文署轄下的香港電影資料館剛於今年1月推出1979年許鞍華首部執導電影《瘋劫》修復版BD。<br />\n剛剛看完整張藍光BD碟，現在來看也感到十分震撼有力，運鏡和剪接都上佳，有些場口更是「去到盡」！或者是因為菲林拍攝的關係，各個演員都交戲十足！<br />\n<br />\n據影碟內說明這片是交托匈牙利電影工作室進行修復，宗旨是以還原當年上映時的感覺為主，所以畫面質素以現今來說不算十分清晰，但也無礙觀感。由於片頭與片尾都已遺失，所以要用Betacam影像片段代替，聲音則翻錄自VHS。我最欣賞是隨碟附送的修復製作特輯，以及刊有影評、海報和劇照的導讀手冊。以$135的價位來說簡直是成本價！讚👍<br />\n<br />\n有興趣的朋友可到電影資料館購買<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/CE/CulturalService/HKFA/zh_TW/web/hkfa/publications_souvenirs/dvd.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2FCE%2FCulturalService%2FHKFA%2Fzh_TW%2Fweb%2Fhkfa%2Fpublications_souvenirs%2Fdvd.html&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu127D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=5115d984\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/CE/CulturalService/HKFA/zh_TW/web/hkfa/publications_souvenirs/dvd.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201902/10/001359mpspghc0n1fpqlpi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201902%2F10%2F001359mpspghc0n1fpqlpi.png&h=0c943615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201902/10/001400sb1rz6xz1jxjj31u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201902%2F10%2F001400sb1rz6xz1jxjj31u.png&h=84a141b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201902/10/001527fa2yokdtahtwiiik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201902%2F10%2F001527fa2yokdtahtwiiik.jpg&h=4d0510ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201902/10/001538qulnuz9wl8dwkchz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201902%2F10%2F001538qulnuz9wl8dwkchz.jpg&h=bdaf20cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201902/10/001614ugle1zr0u0sfg1be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201902%2F10%2F001614ugle1zr0u0sfg1be.jpg&h=96f994a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68b32c261961707123ad1b60c89a12ad76821157","tid":1017513,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"嗰時已經興着襪着高踭鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13966fbf9d1305394aa540f7d7d788d6fc19508","tid":1017513,"uid":71259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"之前係中大睇咗<br />\n好好睇<br />\n完全估唔到由許鞍華拍"},{"pid":"289dca6645690a482f91fa6b78b4e5426a54f60a","tid":1017513,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T22:50:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdfc20986804ee75bda54879f218d7ec6a6d21a0","tid":1017513,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:55:10.000Z","msg":"淨係電影資料館先買到？"},{"pid":"9415c6ff665e8debb79259b3cfd7dc8657d9d8ce","tid":1017513,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13966fbf9d1305394aa540f7d7d788d6fc19508","tid":1017513,"uid":71259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"之前係中大睇咗<br />\n好好睇<br />\n完全估唔到由許鞍華拍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:58:39.000Z","msg":"雖然冇乜恐怖鏡頭但全片充滿恐怖感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good